@Node "Introduction"

 As you may have already noticed, Blanker is no longer Blanker. It
 is now Garshneblanker. I had received numerous suggestions to
 change the name from Blanker to something else, so I finally got
 around to doing it.

 Garshneblanker is an attempt to provide the Amiga community with a
 future compatible, easily expandable screen blanker.

 I would like to provide a platform for others to write custom screen
 blanker modules when the whim strikes and not have to worry about the
 difficulties associated with setting up a Commodities interface and
 dealing with concurrency problems.

@EndNode

